  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 947c76105d7454747a8fc8874cd8bff8, type: 3}
  m_Name: OMorning
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NarrationLines
  lines:
  - Another day, another dollar. I walk into the office again. This time holding
    a cup of coffee in hand.
  - 'This time the space feels less empty, more lived in. I guess I can attribute
    that to myself. I sit down behind the monitor and log in. '
  - "The time reads \u201C5:00am\u201D. I don\u2019t know why I\u2019m here so early.
    I guess my old job just got me used to getting ready while most of the city still
    slept. Probably why I took up excorcism contracts."
  - 'I continue working on the computer. Reading emails, organizing files, all that
    stuff. '
  - "\u201CI might as well get to work.\u201D"
  - I open up the notifications. No reports so far. Makes sense. It is pretty early
    right now. A notification popped up on the screen.
  - Multiple mutilated bodies found underneath a bridge. Mouths all slit.
  - "\u201CSlitmouth? That one doesn\u2019t sound too bad.\u201D"
  - 'I click accept and grab my jacket. Time to get to work. '
  line: 'I click accept and grab my jacket. Time to get to work. '
